# Agent Workflow

Before editing:

1. Read `AGENTS.md`.
2. Read `docs/plan_desarrollo.md`.
3. Read relevant `docs/` and `rules/` files.

During work:

* preserve user changes
* do not refactor unrelated code
* keep plugin package separate from repository support files
* update documentation when project behavior or structure changes
* keep UI text translatable

Before finishing:

* summarize changed files
* report tests run or not run
* report QGIS 3/4 or i18n risks
